flowchart TD
    Start([Start]) --> Init[Rough Goal & Personal Context]
    Init --> InitPrompt[Initial Context Prompt]

    InitPrompt --> KB{Known Content?}

    %% Knowledge Base Building
    KB -->|No or Partial| Search[Search Content Prompt]
    Search --> Curate[Review, Classify, Verify Access]
    Curate --> KBReady

    KB -->|Yes| Upload[Check Context & Upload]
    Upload --> KBReady

    KBReady[Knowledge Base Ready Prompt] --> Refine1[Refine Learning Goal]

    %% Optional Exploration
    Refine1 --> Explore{Optional: 80/20 Exploration?}
    Explore -.->|Yes| Insights[Top 5 Insights & Surprises]
    Insights -.-> Refine2[Notes & Refine Goal]
    Refine2 -.-> Assessment

    Explore -->|No| Assessment[Self-Assessment Phase]

    %% Self Assessment
    Assessment --> AssSetup[Socratic Teacher & Validation Setup]
    AssSetup --> AssQ[10 Assessment Questions with Perfection Game]
    AssQ --> AssSum[Summary of Gaps & Strengths]
    AssSum --> DefineL[Fine-tune Detailed Goals]

    %% Socratic Learning
    DefineL --> Path[Socratic Learning Phase]
    Path --> Priorities[Set Priorities & Create 4Cs Path]
    Priorities --> Session[Run 4Cs Session: Connection, Concept, Practice, Conclusion]

    %% Optional Tracking
    Session -.-> Flashcards([Optional: Anki Flashcards])
    Session -.-> Notes([Optional: Cornell Notes / Mind Maps])

    %% Iteration and End
    Session --> Next{More Sessions?}
    Next -->|Yes| Session
    Next -->|No| Continue{Continue Learning?}

    Continue -.->|Extend Plan| Priorities
    Continue -.->|Deliberate Practice| Practice[Practice Hard Topics]
    Continue -.->|Free Chat| Deepen[Chat to Deepen Understanding]
    Continue -->|Stop| Finish([End])
    
    %% Styling for optional blocks
    classDef optional fill:#f9f9f9,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5,stroke-width:2px;
    class Explore,Insights,Refine2,Flashcards,Notes,Practice,Deepen optional;
